@model IEnumerable<Ecommerce.ViewModels.HangHoaVM>
<h6> Có @Model.Count() Top 10 sản phẩm có lượt mua nhiều nhất  </h6>
<div class="vesitable">
    <div class="owl-carousel vegetable-carousel justify-content-center">

        @foreach (var item in Model)
        {
            <div class="border border-primary rounded position-relative vesitable-item">

                <div class="vesitable-img">
                    <a asp-action="Detail" asp-controller="HangHoa" asp-route-id="@item.MaHh">
                        <img src="~/Hinh/HangHoa/@item.Hinh" class="img-fluid w-100 rounded-top" alt="@item.TenHH">
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div class="text-white bg-primary px-3 py-1 rounded position-absolute" style="top: 10px; right: 10px;">@item.TenLoai</div>
                <div class="p-4 pb-0 rounded-bottom">
                    <a asp-action="Detail" asp-controller="HangHoa" asp-route-id="@item.MaHh">
                        <h4>@item.TenHH</h4>
                    </a>
                    <p>@item.MoTaNgan</p>
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between flex-lg-wrap">
                        <p class="text-dark fs-5 fw-bold mb-0">@item.DonGia</p>
                        <a asp-action="AddToCart" asp-controller="Cart" asp-route-id="@item.MaHh" class="btn border border-secondary rounded-pill px-3 py-1 mb-4 text-primary"><i class="fa fa-shopping-bag me-2 text-primary"></i> Giỏ Hàng </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        }
    </div>
</div>